    • enPassant

      public static boolean enPassant​(String oldPosition, String newPosition)
      Allows for an En Passant Pawn move, if applicable. Only applies if an opponent Pawn has moved two steps in its last move, and the intended capturer Pawn is to either the immediate left or right of the opponent Pawn.
      Parameters:
      oldPosition - Inputs the previous position of the capturer Pawn
      newPosition - Inputs the intended new position of the capturer Pawn
      Returns:
      true if the capturer Pawn is successfully able to perform an En Passant, false if not
